On the part of the umbrella organisation Fecasarm (with associations such as the Bar, Restaurant and Leisure Association of Barcelona), the vice-president, Enric Gomà, trusts to see the end of the tunnel and notes that reservations are quite "lively" overall, although customers "get the maximum out of it".
However, the fun of partying has not decreased, no matter who pays.
Pakistan's nuclear program causes great concern in the US
Islamabad produces nuclear weapons "faster than any other country."
Wikileaks revelations confirm ties between the Taliban and Pakistan.
The content of the correspondence between the North American embassy in Pakistan and the US state department, revealed by Wikileaks, confirms the enormous concern about Washington's nuclear program.
