"Pakistan must hire devout personnel to guard the nuclear facilities; due to the low level of education and culture, extremist organizations have more opportunities to reclassify people involved in nuclear or missile programs," Yuri Korolev of the Russian Foreign Ministry said in a meeting with his North American counterparts.
